Strategic Blueprint for the Executive Functioning Institute
Canonical Further Sources Compilation
Last integrated: February 15, 2026

Purpose
- Centralize authoritative EF resources across Barkley, Brown, Dawson/Guare, and Ward/Jacobsen.
- Map each source to curriculum, intervention, and business implementation pages.

Core Integration Tracks
1) Barkley: Inhibition model, time blindness, evidence-based treatment standards.
2) Brown: Six-cluster cognitive model and internal experience of executive dysfunction.
3) Dawson/Guare: 11 executive skills and skill-specific intervention planning.
4) Ward/Jacobsen: 360 Thinking and Get Ready * Do * Done visual-spatial planning.

