- 30 Essential Ideas, 5A ADHD is Time Blindness: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wmV8HQUuPEk
- 30 Essential Ideas, 7B The 30% Rule: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4OVS16Abo80
